<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invoice</title>

    <style>
        html body {
            zoom: 95%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .invoice-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            height: 160px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 50%;
            float: left;
        }

        .company-info {
            width: 50%;
            text-align: left;
            float: right;
        }

        .company-info h3 {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            color: red;
        }

        .company-info p {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .invoice-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid;
            height: 110px;
            line-height: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .invoice-detail .col-1 {
            width: 35%;
            float: left;
            font-weight: 400;
            padding-left: 1%;
        }

        .invoice-detail .col-2 {
            width: 30%;
            float: left;
            font-weight: 400;
            border-left: 1px solid #000;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            height: 110px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: red;
        }

        .invoice-detail .col-3 {
            width: 34%;
            float: right;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .invoice-eye {
            width: 100%;
            padding-top: 1%;
        }

        .eye-container th,
        .eye-container td , .prodcut-container th, .prodcut-container td,.fool-container th{
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .invoice-prodcut{
            width: 100%;
            padding-top: 1%;
        }

        .invoice-footer{
            width: 100%;
            padding-top: 1%;
            font-size: 14px;
            
        }

        .invoice-footer .foo1{
            width: 65%;
            float: left;
            
        }
        .invoice-footer .foo1 p{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
           line-height: 20px;
           font-size: 14px;

        }
      

        .invoice-footer .foo2{
            width: 34%;
            text-align: center;
            float: right;
            
        }

        .invoice-footer .foo2 table tr th,table tr td{
            padding: 2px !important;
          
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <section class="invoice-header">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="<%= data.LogoURL %>" alt="LOGO" <% %> style="width: <%= data.ImageWidth %>; height: <%=
                    data.ImageHeight %>;">
        </div>
        <div class="company-info">
            <h3>SAIDRUSHTI NETRASEVA CHASHMAGHAR</h3>
            <h3>AKOLE</h3>
            <p>ADDRESS-SHOP NO 2, BACK SIDE OF VISION EYEPLUS, BEHIND BUS STAND. A-P/TALK - AKOLE, DIST- AHILYANAGAR,
                PIN 422601</p>
            <p>MB 9136529393, GMAIL-RAJVEERAHER@GMAIL.COM</p>
            <p>GST NO-27AMHPA7559D1Z3</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="invoice-detail">
        <table class="col-1">
            <tr>
                <% if (data.bill !=='Tax Invoice' ){%>
                <td>ORDER NO- <%=data.billMaster.InvoiceNo%></td>
                <%}%>
                <% if (data.bill ==='Tax Invoice' ){%>
                <td>INVOICE NO- <%=data.billMaster.InvoiceNo%></td>
                <%}%>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>NAME- <%=data.customer.Title%> <%=data.customer.Name%></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>ADDRESS- <%=data.customer.Address%> </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>AGE- <%=data.customer.Age%></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>MB NO- <%=data.customer.MobileNo1%></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <table class="col-2">
            <tr>
                <th style="text-transform: uppercase !important;"><%=data.bill%></th>
            </tr>
            <% if (data.ShowPower === true){%>
            <tr>
                <th>REFRACTIVE ERROR</th>
            </tr>
            <%}%>
        </table>
        <table class="col-3">
            <tr>
                <td>ORDER DATE- <%=data.billMaster.BillDate%></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>DELIVERD DATE- <%=data.billMaster.DeliveryDate%></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>SALES PERSON- <%=data.employee%></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>LOYALTI POINT- </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>REMARK- </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

    </section>
    <% if (data.ShowPower === true){%>
    <section class="invoice-eye">
        <% if(data.EyeMeasurement !== null && data.EyeMeasurement.length !== 0){ data.EyeMeasurement.forEach(function (i, index) { %>
        <table class="eye-container" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
            <tr>
                <th>EYE</th>
                <th>SPH</th>
                <th>CYL</th>
                <th>AXIS</th>
                <th>DIST VISION</th>
                <th>ADD</th>
                <th>NEAR VISION</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>RE</td>
                <td><%=i.REDPSPH%></td>
                <td><%=i.REDPCYL%> </td>
                <td><%=i.REDPAxis%> </td>
                <td><%=i.REDPVA%></td>
                <td><%=i.R_Addition%> </td>
                <td><%=i.RENPVA%></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>LE</td>
                <td><%=i.LEDPSPH%></td>
                <td><%=i.LEDPCYL%> </td>
                <td><%=i.LEDPAxis%></td>
                <td><%=i.LEDPVA%></td>
                <td><%=i.L_Addition%></td>
                <td><%=i.LENPVA%> </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <%})}%>
    </section>
    <%}%>

    <section class="invoice-prodcut">
        <table class="prodcut-container" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
            <tr>
                <th>SR NO</th>
                <th>HSN CODE</th>
                <th>DESCRIPTION</th>
                <th>QUANTITY</th>
                <th>RATE</th>
                <th>DISC</th>
                <th>SUB TOTAL</th>
                <% if (data.shopdetails.Tax==="true" &&  data.bill==='Tax Invoice' ){%>
                <th>CGST 
                    <% if (data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'FRAME' || data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'LENS' || data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'CONTACT LENS'){%>
                      6%
                    <%}%>
                    <% if (data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'SUNGLASS'){%>
                        9%
                      <%}%>
                </th>
                <th>SGST 
                    <% if (data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'FRAME' || data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'LENS' || data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'CONTACT LENS'){%>
                        6%
                      <%}%>
                      <% if (data.billItemList[0].ProductTypeName == 'SUNGLASS'){%>
                        9%
                      <%}%>
                </th>
                <%}%>
                <th>NET AMT</th>
            </tr>
            <% if(data.billItemList.length != 0 ){ data.billItemList.forEach(function (i, index) { %>
            <tr>
                <td><%=index+1%></td>
                <td><%= i.HSNCode %></td>
                <td>
                    <%= i.ProductName %>  
                    <% if (i.Warranty != '' && i.Warranty != "undefined"){%>
                       /<%= i.Warranty %>
                    <%}%>
                    <% if (i.Remark != '' && i.Remark != "undefined"){%>
                        /<%= i.Remark %>
                    <%}%>
                </td>
                <td><%= i.Quantity %></td>
                <td><%= i.UnitPrice %></td>
                <td><%= i.DiscountAmount %></td>
                <td><%= i.SubTotal %></td>
                <% if (data.shopdetails.Tax==="true" &&  data.bill==='Tax Invoice' ){%>
                <td><%= i.GSTAmount %></td>
                <td><%= i.GSTAmount %></td>
                <%}%>
                <td><%= i.TotalAmount %></td>
            </tr>
            <%})}%>
            <tr class="total">
                <td colspan="3">TOTAL</td>
                <td><%= data.billMaster.Quantity %></td>
                <td><%= data.totalUnits %></td>
                <td style="color: red;"><%= data.totalDiscounts %></td>
                <td><%= data.billMaster.SubTotal %></td>
                <% if (data.shopdetails.Tax==="true" &&  data.bill==='Tax Invoice' ){%>
                <td><%= data.billMaster.GSTAmount/2 %></td>
                <td><%= data.billMaster.GSTAmount/2 %></td>
                <%}%>
                <td style="color: red"><%= data.billMaster.TotalAmount %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </section>


    <section class="invoice-footer " >
        <% if (data.bill !== 'Tax Invoice' ){%>
        <div class="foo1" style="border: 1px solid #000;text-transform: lowercase;">
            <p>* Please collect your spect within 15 days from the date of order.</p>
            <p>*Delay in delivery due to any technical problem is acceptable.</p>
            <p>*Once an order is placed it can not be cancelled.</p>
            <p>*Advance once given will not be returned.</p>
            <p>*At list 50% advance is required.</p>
            <p>*Repairing is on customers responsibility.</p>
            <p>*We will not responsible for breackage of frames or glasses while shifting new glasses in to old frame or old glasses in to new frame.</p>
        </div>
        <%}%>
        <% if (data.bill === 'Tax Invoice' ){%>
        <div class="foo1" style="border: 1px solid #000; text-transform:lowercase;">
            <p>*ANY FRAMES, SUNGLASSES OR LENSES OF THE LOCAL COMPANY WILL NOT HAVE ANY KIND OF WARRANTY</p>
            <p>*Before delivered you should check your spect or sunglasses properly there is no any complaint accepted after buying sunglassas or spectacle.</p>
            <p>*If you are using a spectacle for the first time or if there is any changes of spectacle power, it may take at list 15 days time to comfirt it.</p>
            <p>*BREAKAGE & SCRATCHES WILL NOT CONSIDER UNDER WARRANRY </p>
        </div>
        <%}%>
        <div class="foo2" >
            <table class="fool-container" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; position: relative; height: 100px;">
                <tr>
                    <th>PAYABLE AMT</th>
                    <th> <%= data.billMaster.TotalAmount %></th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>PAID  AMT</th>
                    <th><%= data.recivePayment.toFixed(2) %></th>
                </tr>
                <% if (data.bill !== 'Tax Invoice' ){%>
                <tr>
                    <th>BALANCE AMT</th>
                    <th>  <%= data.CurrentInvoiceBalance %></th>
                </tr>
                <%}%>
                <tr>
                    <th>PAYMENT MODE</th>
                    <th>
                    <% if(data.paidlist.length !==0){ data.paidlist.forEach(function (i, index) { %>
                        <% if (i.PaymentMode !=='Payment Initiated' ){%>
                             <%=i.PaymentMode%>/
                        <%}%>
                    <%})}%>
                </th>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; border: 1px solid #000; width: 33%; height: 80px;">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 10%;">
                    SIGN <br> SAIDRUSHTI NETRASEVA CHASHMAGHAR <br> PROP. SACHIN AHER  (CONSULTANT OPTOMETRIST)
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>